https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7f5e5bfeca6e4106483d2e115e8ba896","url_token":"min-rui-de-shan-dian-lu-wei","name":"敏锐的闪电芦苇","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2197c44c6edec25756e9fe711fa4f3c5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2197c44c6edec25756e9fe711fa4f3c5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7f5e5bfeca6e4106483d2e115e8ba896","user_type":"people","headline":"知乎大透明","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560829826","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545891622,"updated_time":1545891622,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e惊闻又一高中生自称能够证明哥德巴赫猜想，深感长江后浪推前浪。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了众多答案，许多答案几近冷嘲热讽。很多人都在笑，我却笑不出来，眼泪往肚子里咽。因为，一个国家没有人才是可怕的，有人才没被发现是可悲的，但发现了人才却对其进行嘲讽就是可耻了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，证明不是乱证，猜想不是乱猜。连陈景润老先生都说，只用初等数论的知识是无法解决哥德巴赫猜想的；但你如果一定要告诉我们你可以“骑自行车上月球”，结果我们看到你是骑自行车上了一个写着“月”字的球，那么你作为证明者是要向本国人民谢罪的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管结果怎样，我都希望题主能够给各位一个交代，毕竟证明哥德巴赫猜想是具有世界级影响力的事情，不可儿戏。就算题主失败了，也不要气馁。有勇气去证明哥德巴赫猜想的，想必已有比较扎实的数学功底和强大的数学思维。希望题主日后苦练七十二变，笑对八十一难。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到八十一难，我就想起我国四大名著之一《西游记》。明年下半年，中美合拍，正式开机，弘扬中华文化，文体两开花，多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别处看到的段子，侵删\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559236743,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559236743","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545709227,"updated_time":1545709227,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个问题没有意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e清华北大作为分数线最高的两所学校，能考上的人很少，于是有人通过各种方式保送进入，在试卷之外取胜，算是一种降维打击，像以前的各种特长就是这样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但这些途径，最终只是追求一个入学的资格而已，而入学的资格，又只是为学术研究的第一步开了一道小门，走清华北大的门要比其他门离学术高峰更近，但也近的有限。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而哥德巴赫猜想，本身就是学术高峰上的明珠，你如果能摘下它，说明已经在山顶了，还需要考虑能不能进入口处的那扇小门吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你能独立地完成它的证明，高考对你根本就不是任何问题，也不会来提这种问，如果连高考题对你来说都有困难，却梦想着直接证明哥德巴赫猜想来绕过它，也只能是白日梦而已。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561660814,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"eb0373022fb3f70ffd1a6ff469fff2b8","url_token":"wang-da-ke-53-61","name":"王大可Wongdark","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6b93993ac8dd384568e3eb4d2c5863bb_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6b93993ac8dd384568e3eb4d2c5863bb_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/eb0373022fb3f70ffd1a6ff469fff2b8","user_type":"people","headline":"不如作蜉蝣麻衣霜染淋漓死生\n恣朝暮 彀长空","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561660814","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7b9309e3f952720ddb16619ab9b6d3cb_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545987055,"updated_time":1545987057,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteu